You play with action figures?

14:40.123 --> 14:41.163
Yeah.

14:41.169 --> 14:42.623
They're cooler than Hot Wheels

14:42.625 --> 14:44.024
and not as labor-intensive as Legos.

14:44.026 --> 14:45.726
I think we should find your parents.

14:45.728 --> 14:47.128
Even though you and I have history

14:47.130 --> 14:48.793
with me delivering you chicken and such,

14:48.799 --> 14:50.389
if we get pulled over with a missing

14:50.395 --> 14:51.993
child in the back of our van,

14:52.268 --> 14:53.934
I predict a lot of mayhem,

14:53.936 --> 14:55.436
and quite possibly some tazing

14:55.438 --> 14:56.537
before the truth surfaces.

15:05.548 --> 15:07.716
You're gonna smoke right now?

15:08.223 --> 15:09.603
It's medicinal.

15:09.609 --> 15:11.221
What I thought was going to be

15:11.227 --> 15:12.660
a tranquil drive to the mountains

15:12.666 --> 15:15.000
has developed into an
accidental kidnapping.

15:18.561 --> 15:20.995
I hope this smoke isn't
getting back there.

15:20.997 --> 15:23.898
You're not suddenly hungry
for no reason, are you?

15:23.900 --> 15:24.965
No.

15:26.769 --> 15:29.303
You're a brave little dude
to be out all by yourself.

15:29.305 --> 15:31.605
First time my parents
left me home alone,

15:31.607 --> 15:33.574
I hid under the covers the whole time.

15:33.576 --> 15:35.497
- Really?
- Oh, yeah.

15:35.503 --> 15:36.932
We had a water heater in the basement

15:36.938 --> 15:38.204
that sounded like a ghost.

15:39.916 --> 15:41.449
Hey, man!

15:41.556 --> 15:42.788
What did I tell you about

15:42.794 --> 15:44.127
making ghost sounds when I'm high?

15:44.159 --> 15:45.525
But I like making ghost sounds,

15:45.527 --> 15:46.993
and you're always high,

15:46.995 --> 15:49.062
which leaves me no window
to make ghost sounds.

15:49.064 --> 15:50.724
Ghosts aren't real.

15:50.730 --> 15:52.298
How do you know?

15:52.300 --> 15:54.300
- My dad told me.
- See?

15:54.302 --> 15:56.336
Even the little boy knows you're crazy.

16:01.105 --> 16:02.892
Okay, Mr. Ghost Expert.

16:02.898 --> 16:04.611
What are your views on Santa Claus?

16:04.613 --> 16:05.814
He comes down the chimney and

16:05.820 --> 16:07.347
leaves you presents if you're good.

16:07.349 --> 16:09.415
- That's bullshit.
- Hey, man!

16:13.410 --> 16:15.855
Can I talk to you outside for a second?

16:15.857 --> 16:17.188
What are you doing?

16:17.194 --> 16:19.259
You can't tell a kid
there's no Santa Claus.

16:19.261 --> 16:21.427
Okay, first of all, I'm high.

16:21.433 --> 16:23.790
You have to take that into account
when judging my behavior.

16:23.796 --> 16:25.827
- Fair enough.
- And second of all,

16:25.833 --> 16:27.233
you guys were ganging up on me.

16:27.239 --> 16:29.357
- My back was against the wall.
- That's true.

16:29.363 --> 16:32.122
We were ganging up on you.
That's my bad.

16:32.366 --> 16:33.798
Let me hit that.

16:39.339 --> 16:40.643
I just want you

16:40.649 --> 16:42.149
to get over your fear of ghosts

16:42.155 --> 16:44.106
so you don't have to sleep
with the dome light on.

16:44.311 --> 16:47.235
We can't keep jump-sing every morning.

17:27.984 --> 17:30.051
- Kid?
