18:13.735 --> 18:14.932
That's mine, buddy.

18:14.938 --> 18:17.137
You're not supposed to
play with action figures.

18:17.139 --> 18:19.048
And you're not supposed to be scared.

18:19.054 --> 18:20.407
Hey, man!

18:20.409 --> 18:21.984
What did I tell you about making

18:21.990 --> 18:23.410
