18:23.412 --> 18:25.745
But grown-ups do all those things.

18:25.747 --> 18:27.447
So maybe my dad was wrong.

18:30.385 --> 18:34.087
Maybe you can do all
that and still be a man.

18:34.089 --> 18:36.256
Maybe I was already a man.

18:37.292 --> 18:39.225
The only thing I know for sure

18:39.227 --> 18:41.561
