Santa Claus isn't real.

18:53.375 --> 18:54.808
See?

18:54.810 --> 18:57.177
Told you he'd be fine.

18:58.346 --> 19:00.313
He smells a little like weed, though.

19:00.315 --> 19:02.515
Probably 'cause we left the window open.

19:02.517 --> 19:03.853
You were right.

19:03.859 --> 19:05.568
I guess it's just hard for me to accept

19:05.574 --> 19:07.141
